node.text:
🍴 New Specials! 🍴 Head into #MBCWaikiki or #MBCKailua to try these new limited-time dishes!

🦐 Spicy Shrimp Ceviche 🦐
Shrimp and Marlin tossed in leche de tigre – a mix of coconut milk, lemon, lime, Aji Amarillo chili, onion, garlic, celery and cilantro. Served with crunchy taro chips and topped with red onion, chilies and cilantro.

🌽 Elote Street Corn 🌽
Local corn cob, grilled, with spicy mayo. Sprinkled with cotija cheese, chopped cilantro, and taco seasoning.

node.text: Go "Against the Grain" with our veggie burger! Black beans, brown rice, mac nuts, carrots, herbs, and flax make up this tasty sando, then topped with avocado, pickled ginger, and vegan mayo. Add a side of fries and a pint of beer for a well-rounded meal. 😋 🍺
